</div><span id="infoPro"></span>
<div class="grayText"><strong>How do we protect visitor information?</strong></div>
<div class="innerText">We do not use vulnerability scanning and/or scanning to PCI standards.</div><div class="innerText">We use regular Malware Scanning.

</div><div class="innerText">We do not use an SSL certificate</div><div class="innerText">Â Â Â Â Â  <strong>â€¢</strong> We only provide articles and information, we never ask for personal or private information like email addresses, or credit card numbers.</div><span id="coUs"></span>
<div class="grayText"><strong>Do we use 'cookies'?</strong></div>
